Package: liblagraph1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: LAGraph runtime library
 LAGraph provides graph algorithms implemented on top of the GraphBLAS API.

Package: liblagraphx1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: LAGraph experimental runtime library
 Experimental graph algorithms and helpers for LAGraph.

Package: liblagraph-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libgraphblas-dev, liblagraph1 (= ${binary:Version}), liblagraphx1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: LAGraph development files
 Headers, pkg-config metadata, CMake config, and linker symlinks for
 LAGraph 1.2.1 and LAGraphX 1.2.1.
